description: Engine account name.
name: account

description: DS engine account ID.
name: accountId

description: Engine account type: Google AdWords, Bing Ads, Yahoo Japan Listing Ads, Yahoo Search Marketing, Yahoo Gemini, Baidu, or Comparison Shopping.
name: accountType

description: DS ad group ID.
name: adGroupId

description: DS ad ID.
name: adId

description: Advertiser name.
name: advertiser

description: For offline conversions, this is an ID provided by advertisers. If an advertiser doesn't specify such an ID, DoubleClick Search generates one. For online conversions, this is equal to the conversionId column or the floodlightOrderId column depending on the advertiser's Floodlight instructions.
name: advertiserConversionId

description: DS advertiser ID.
name: advertiserId

description: Agency name.
name: agency

description: DS agency ID.
name: agencyId

description: DS campaign ID.
name: campaignId

description: What the conversion is attributed to: Visit or Keyword+Ad.
name: conversionAttributionType

description: The date, in the DFA network time zone, when the conversion occurred. This date is used for conversion metric aggregation. For example, when DS aggregates actions for May 1, it counts all action conversions whose conversionDate is May 1.
name: conversionDate

description: ID that DoubleClick Search generates for each conversion.
name: conversionId

description: The UTC timestamp of the conversion's most recent modification.
name: conversionLastModifiedTimestamp

description: The quantity of items recorded by the conversion, as determined by the qtyparameter. The advertiser is responsible for dynamically populating the parameter (such as number of items sold in the conversion), otherwise it defaults to 1.
name: conversionQuantity

description: The total dollar amount from the conversion.
name: conversionRevenue

description: The search term that led to the conversion.
name: conversionSearchTerm

description: The UTC timestamp when the conversion occurred.
name: conversionTimestamp

description: The type of the conversion: Action or Transaction.
name: conversionType

description: A unique string, for the visit that the conversion is attributed to, that is passed to the landing page as the gclid URL parameter. Only enabled for advertisers with conversion API integration or Google Analytics integration.
name: conversionVisitExternalClickId

description: The DS visit ID that the conversion is attributed to.
name: conversionVisitId

description: The UTC timestamp of the visit that the conversion is attributed to.
name: conversionVisitTimestamp

description: The device segment that the conversion is attributed to: Desktop, Mobile, Tablet, or Other.
name: deviceSegment

description: The ID of the feed table associated with this conversion.
name: feedId

description: The ID of the feed item row associated with this conversion.
name: feedItemId

description: The type of feed associated with this conversion.
name: feedType

description: Floodlight activity name.
name: floodlightActivity

description: DS Floodlight activity ID.
name: floodlightActivityId

description: Floodlight activity tag.
name: floodlightActivityTag

description: The Floodlight request string of the conversion.
name: floodlightEventRequestString

description: Floodlight group name.
name: floodlightGroup

description: The type of conversions generated by Floodlight activities in this group: Action or Transaction.
name: floodlightGroupConversionType

description: DS Floodlight group ID.
name: floodlightGroupId

description: Floodlight group tag.
name: floodlightGroupTag

description: The Floodlight order ID provided by the advertiser for the conversion.
name: floodlightOrderId

description: The original, unchanged revenue associated with the Floodlight event, before Floodlight currency instruction modifications.
name: floodlightOriginalRevenue

description: The Floodlight referrer website of the conversion.
name: floodlightReferrer

description: The DS inventory account ID containing the product associated with the conversion. DS generates this ID when you link an inventory account in DS.
name: inventoryAccountId

description: DS keyword ID.
name: keywordId

description: The sales channel of the product associated with the conversion: Online or Local.
name: productChannel

description: The country (ISO 3166 format) registered for the inventory feed that contains the product associated with this conversion.
name: productCountry

description: The product group ID associated with this conversion. Only conversions from shopping campaigns have product group IDs. Product group IDs should not be used for joining.
name: productGroupId

description: The ID of the product associated with this conversion.
name: productId

description: The language (ISO 639-1) of the product associated this conversion.
name: productLanguage

description: The store in the Local Inventory Ad associated with the conversion. This should match the store IDs used in your local products feed.
name: productStoreId

description: DS product target ID.
name: productTargetId

description: The status of the conversion: Active or Removed.
name: status
